    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-05-13T02:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-05-13T02:35:00-05:00" n="703"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d703">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 891.48/48</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CJL1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caldwell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-05-13T11:00:00+03:25">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 13, 1918, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received May 14, 9.44 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram 53, May 10, 6 p.m. Needy Jews in Persia estimated thirty to forty
                    thousand of which probably 25 per cent are starving and in dire need.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_CJL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caldwell</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
